# Use case: build the inner images yourself and run against the local images
# (contributors hacking on agentic-dev, air-gapped hosts, or customizing the
# image). No SANDCASTLE_IMAGE override → the orchestrator defaults to
# sandcastle:local / sandcastle-opencode:local.
# Copy to .sandcastle/orchestrator.env and fill GH_TOKEN.

# Orchestrator's gh token (issue list/label/comment, PR create). Host: `gh auth token`.
GH_TOKEN=

# (No image overrides — defaults to the locally-built images. To customize the
#  image per project, build with --build-arg AGENTIC_PROJECT=<name>.)
